  schema:name "Discworld MUD Messaging Systems" ;
  schema:description "Survey of Discworld MUD's layered communication architecture: say and tell commands as room-scoped and direct messaging; shout for distance communication; the talker system for out-of-character channels; and soul commands for social broadcasting. Maps Discworld's message-routing patterns onto the 561 messaging-foundations spec." ;
